---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout title="APIs - Documentacao" adm={true} activePage="/admin/docs">
  <div class="docs-layout">
    <aside class="docs-sidebar">
      <nav class="docs-nav">
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Getting Started</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs">Visao Geral</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/structure">Estrutura</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Sistema</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/auth">Autenticacao</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/store">Loja e Carrinho</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/ai">Inteligencia Artificial</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Backend</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/database">Banco de Dados</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/api" class="active">APIs</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Configuracao</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/env">Variaveis de Ambiente</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/commands">Comandos</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="docs-content">
      <h1><Icon name="lucide:webhook" size={24} /> Rotas de API</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        O projeto utiliza Astro API routes para endpoints server-side, Alem de server actions
        para formulários e interacoes complexas.
      </p>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:folder" size={20} /> Estrutura de Rotas</h2>
      <div class="files-list">
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:folder" size={16} />
          <code>src/pages/api/</code>
          <span>API routes (SSR)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:folder" size={16} />
          <code>src/pages/api/auth/</code>
          <span>Endpoints de autenticacao</span>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:folder" size={16} />
          <code>src/pages/api/cart/</code>
          <span>Endpoints do carrinho</span>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:folder" size={16} />
          <code>src/actions/</code>
          <span>Server actions</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:lock" size={20} /> Autenticacao Owner</h2>
      <div class="endpoint-card">
        <div class="method post">POST</div>
        <code>/api/auth/owner/login</code>
      </div>
      <p>Faz login com email e senha. Retorna cookie de sessao.</p>

      <pre>{'{'}
  "email": "admin@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha123"
{'}'}</pre>

      <div class="endpoint-card">
        <div class="method post">POST</div>
        <code>/api/auth/owner/logout</code>
      </div>
      <p>Remove cookie de sessao.</p>

      <div class="endpoint-card">
        <div class="method get">GET</div>
        <code>/api/auth/owner/session</code>
      </div>
      <p>Retorna dados da sessao atual ou 401 se nao autenticado.</p>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:shopping-cart" size={20} /> Carrinho</h2>
      <div class="endpoint-card">
        <div class="method get">GET</div>
        <code>/api/cart</code>
      </div>
      <p>Retorna itens do carrinho. Atualmente usa localStorage (placeholder para sync).</p>

      <div class="endpoint-card">
        <div class="method post">POST</div>
        <code>/api/cart</code>
      </div>
      <p>Adiciona item ao carrinho.</p>

      <pre>{'{'}
  "productId": "uuid-do-produto",
  "name": "Nome do Produto",
  "price": 9990,
  "quantity": 1,
  "image": "/images/produto.jpg"
{'}'}</pre>

      <div class="endpoint-card">
        <div class="method put">PUT</div>
        <code>/api/cart/[productId]</code>
      </div>
      <p>Atualiza quantidade de um item.</p>

      <pre>{'{'}
  "quantity": 3
{'}'}</pre>

      <div class="endpoint-card">
        <div class="method delete">DELETE</div>
        <code>/api/cart/[productId]</code>
      </div>
      <p>Remove item do carrinho.</p>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:shield-check" size={20} /> Boas Praticas de Seguranca</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Validacao de Input:</strong> Use Zod schemas para validar todos os dados de entrada</li>
        <li><strong>Rate Limiting:</strong> Limite requisicoes por IP para prevenir ataques</li>
        <li><strong>Headers Seguros:</strong> Implemente CORS, CSP, X-Frame-Options</li>
        <li><strong>Tratamento de Erros:</strong> Nunca exponha stack traces em producao</li>
        <li><strong>Autenticacao:</strong> Valide sessoes em todas as rotas protegidas</li>
      </ul>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={20} /> Formato de Resposta</h2>
      <pre>{'{'}"success": true,
  "data": {'{'} ... {'}'}
{'}'}

{'{'}"success": false,
  "error": "Mensagem de erro"
{'}'}</pre>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:zap" size={20} /> Server Actions</h2>
      <p>O projeto tambem utiliza Astro server actions para operacoes complexas:</p>
      <div class="files-list">
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/actions/auth.ts</code>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/actions/cart.ts</code>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/actions/product.ts</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs-layout {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 70px auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .docs-sidebar {
    width: 260px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 90px;
    height: fit-content;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 110px);
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .docs-nav {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .docs-nav-section a {
    display: block;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-sm);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .docs-nav-section a:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-10);
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .docs-nav-section a.active {
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-20);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .docs-content {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .docs-content h1 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content h1 svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .docs-content h2 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary-alpha-20);
  }

  .docs-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .docs-content h2 svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .docs-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .docs-content p {
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content code {
    font-family: monospace;
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-10);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 0.2em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .docs-content pre {
    background: var(--color-gray-900);
    color: #f8f8f2;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .docs-content ul {
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .endpoint-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .method {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .method.get {
    background: #10b981;
    color: white;
  }

  .method.post {
    background: #3b82f6;
    color: white;
  }

  .method.put {
    background: #f59e0b;
    color: white;
  }

  .method.delete {
    background: #ef4444;
    color: white;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
  }

  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '->';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .files-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .file-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.875rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .file-item svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .file-item code {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .file-item span {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .docs-layout {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .docs-sidebar {
      width: 100%;
      position: static;
    }

    .docs-nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-nav,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h1,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h2,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h3 {
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content p,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content li {
    color: #a0a0a0;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .file-item {
    background: #252525;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .file-item code {
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .endpoint-card {
    background: #252525;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .method.get {
    background: #059669;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .method.post {
    background: #2563eb;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .method.put {
    background: #d97706;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .method.delete {
    background: #dc2626;
  }
</style>
